{
  "stem": "2684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, we were-- I was so cold that I just couldn't stand it out in the quarry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I pinched two bags of cement-- bags, the papers only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I put it underneath to keep me warm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I forgot to take it off when I left work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they found it on the way back because I was a little bit chestier than when I left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got a punishment, 25 lashes, front of the-- front of the Fluechtling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I can't remember more than five or six because I, I passed out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the lashes was because if we put bags on us, the lices will get us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the paper get lice from us, not we get lice from the paper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So for about two or three days, I couldn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this little Wehrmacht sergeant or whatever was his-- he came into the lager looking for me why I wasn't working for two, three days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he found me in my block with bruises and whatever you get from six lashes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The guys told me I got only six, because I can't remember too much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they wanted to show to the rest of them that you don't put-- it's like a punishment front of everybody.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came in, and he brought a piece of bread, and told that German guy who was the blockalteste or a kapo who was the meanest things, a sadist-- a definite sadist because he did things to us which I don't even think the Germans would ask him to do.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a German prisoner, of criminal or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He made us run barefoot at 2 o'clock the night, naked in the block, all of us.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
